I"Ð<p>The twisted cubic.</p>

<p>Get the equation of the tangent variety to the twisted cubic, using M2.</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>i1 : R = QQ[X,Y,Z];

i2 : S = QQ[s,t];

i3 : f = map(S,R,matrix {{t+s, t^2 + 2*s*t, t^3 + 3*s*t^2}});

o3 : RingMap S &lt;--- R

i4 : ker f

             2 2     3      3             2
o4 = ideal(3X Y  - 4X Z - 4Y  + 6X*Y*Z - Z )

o4 : Ideal of R
</code></pre></div></div>

